data.description: Welcome home to this charming Cape Cod style residence nestled on a peaceful, tree-lined street in a highly sought after school district. Boasting incredible curb appeal, this delightful home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a home office, and an array of desirable features that every homeowner dreams of. As you step inside you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with sleek granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The large cozy living room provides plenty of space for entertaining. The office space provides a private escape to accomplish work. A true highlight of this property is the enchanting fenced-in backyard, providing a safe haven for family and pets to play freely. Spend sunny afternoons relishing in the privacy and serenity of the stunning wooded area which surrounds the home. For those seeking relaxation, the large covered front porch offers the perfect spot to enjoy a morning coffee or watch captivating sunsets. This home truly offers it all. Call today to schedule your private showing!
